Fox News cancels the Republican debate scheduled for Monday in Salt Lake City, Utah. The Utah Republican Party has received more than 50,000 ticket requests. Utah Lieutenant Governor Spencer Cox is upset Trump, "...is snubbing the state of Utah." According to Deseret News, Trump is in fourth place in Utah polls. (The Salt Lake Tribune) (Deseret News)Republican Party voters, in precinct gatherings, hold the Nevada caucuses with Donald Trump winning, Marco Rubio coming second, and Ted Cruz finishing in third place. (ABC 7), (Washington Examiner), Oregon Live)